in the development of software productivity products for mobile devices such as tablets and smartphones and application publishing software solutions it operates through the following segments goglobal and hopto the goglobal segment includes all available versions of the goglobal family of products oem private labeling kits software developers kits maintenance contracts and product training and support the hopto segment provides mobile endusers with a productivity workspace for mobile devices that allows to manage share view and edit documents the company was founded by walter keller in 98 and is headquartered in campbell ca valuation pe current  pe ratio with extraordinary items  price to sales ratio 9 enterprise value to ebitda  enterprise value to sales  total debt to enterprise value 3 efficiency revenueemployee 8 income per employee 94 receivables turnover  total asset turnover 4 liquidity current ratio 8 quick ratio 8 cash ratio  profitability gross margin 3 operating margin 46 pretax margin 4 net margin  return on assets  capital structure total debt to total assets  officers and executives name age officer since title mr eldad eilam   president chief executive officer  director mr jeanlouis casabonne 8 4 chief financial officer  secretary mr ashfaq a munshi 4 4 director mr sam m auriemma   chairman mr jeremy e verba 3  independent director insider actions – purchase – sale  – number of transactions for more information visit the ft lexiconlexicon on this pageexplore our toolsalertsdata archiveportfolioworld marketsequities screenerfunds overview  thomson reuters click for restrictions all markets data located on ftcom is subject to the ft terms  conditionsall content on ftcom is for your general information and use only and is not intended to address your particular requirements in particular the content does not constitute any form of advice recommendation representation endorsement or arrangement by ft and is not intended to be relied upon by users in maki